headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid PAYX and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Shareholders of Paychex would probably like to forget the past six months even happened. The stock dropped 28.9% and now trades at $112.51. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
